{"body": "This appears to break ActiveRecord::Base#first and #last.\nIt looks like 13f1401a6cf0266a3b0a91b173f976db2d4e50f3 also needs to be reverted.\n\nTo reproduce the bug:\n\n```ruby\nPost.first #=> nil\npost = Post.create(:name => \"test\")\nPost.first #=> post\npost.destroy\nPost.first #=> post\n```\n\nThe last Post.first should not be returning the destroyed record.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6047749", "created_at": "2012-05-31T21:15:17Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6558#issuecomment-6047749", "updated_at": "2012-05-31T21:15:17Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6558, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tgildea/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tgildea/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tgildea/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/tgildea", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tgildea/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/tgildea", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tgildea/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/2d7f375e2ef2256700f5a38f491606e4?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fd011c7278572db1a43f7df991d2f619f.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tgildea/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tgildea/received_events", "gravatar_id": "2d7f375e2ef2256700f5a38f491606e4", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tgildea/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "tgildea", "type": "User", "id": 109723, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tgildea/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52380689bd3543c15100c93c"}, "id": 6047749, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6558"}
